data.description: A masterpiece of architectural excellence: this stunning 2006 custom-built home is a true testament to luxury and craftsmanship! Privately nestled away on slightly over 1 acre of land in the serene neighborhood of Avon Park Estates in Avon Park, FL - this residence offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and timeless charm. Boasting 4 large bedrooms PLUS office on a split floor plan, 3 full bathrooms, 3+ car garage, and opulent in-ground pool - this home is designed to provide comfort and style for today's discerning homeowner. Arriving at the driveway- the pristine curb appeal offered by the lush landscaping, the stunning Mediterranean influenced architecture, and impeccable grand entryway will make you exited to arrive home! As you enter inside through the lovely double glass panel entryway doors, you'll be greeted by an inviting foyer that flows seamlessly into the front living room and formal dining room impressively adorned with a custom 14 ft. high Box Beam Coffered ceilings, intricate crown molding finishings, and decorative illuminated wall niches. The perfectly distributed layout of the home provide spectacular views of the in-ground concrete pool oasis surrounded by an open concrete patio and covered lanai overlooking the gorgeous fenced-in back yard. Whether you're hosting a summer BBQ or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this outdoor space is sure to impress. Centrally located gourmet kitchen is one to be adored containing all top-of-the-line Stainless Steel appliances, copious amounts of high quality Granite countertops, huge center island with dual wine racks, multi-level glazed solid wood cabinetry, hidden corner pantry, and custom intricate mosaic tile backsplash. The spacious family room also features a cozy bonus room currently in use as an entertaining/wine room offering a warm and inviting atmosphere! The massive primary suite is a sanctuary of relaxation that you will absolutely fall in love with - complete with generous amounts of dual walk-in custom designed closet spaces! The spa-like ensuite bath offers a fully tiled infinity double head shower, luxurious porcelain soak tub, recessed lighting, private commode room, and separate single sink vanities! Each additional bedroom is generously sized and offers its own unique character. Extra convenient in-home utility room with extra storage space and utility sink. Plenty of space for your vehicles is provided in the oversized 768 Square Ft. 3 car garage. Never be left in the dark thanks to a newly installed 24KW automatic full home generator! Brand new custom Plantation Shutters, 3.5 ton multi-zoned HVAC System new in 2021, New shingle roof in 2022, New Vinyl fence in 2021. With over 3,600 living square footage alone and attention to detail at every turn, this custom-built home is the epitome of luxury living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your forever home and experience the unique beauty of this one-of-a-kind residence every day!
